text: Lewis Coady (born 20 September 1976) is an English former professional footballer who played as a midfielder. He made appearances in the English Football League with Wrexham and Doncaster Rovers, however spent most of his career playing in the Welsh Premier League. ==References== Category:1976 births Category:Living people Category:Wrexham A.F.C. players Category:Colwyn Bay F.C. players Category:Doncaster Rovers F.C. players Category:Porthmadog F.C. players Category:Caernarfon Town F.C. players Category:Bangor City F.C. players Category:English footballers Category:Association football midfielders Category:English Football League players
